parameters: Claudia: A monster girl... I wonder.

Shemini: It's been a while since I last
saw humans in this forest...
Shemini: May I ask for your name...?

Claudia: I am Claudia. I have a reason
for searching for the \c[6]resin
gemstones\c[0].

Shemini: In that case, I do have a
few...
Claudia: Can you give it to me?

Shemini: That is a valuable item, so I
can't simply give it away.
Shemini: Why do you need it?

Shemini: I see... For the sake of your
friend...

Shemini: If that's the case, I will
gladly give it to you. Please take it
with you.
Shemini: However, I have one request...
Shemini: Yes, it's for Lady Claudia...

Claudia: What's wrong? Is there
something on my face?
Shemini: That's a very lovely name♥
Shemini: I can't bear it anymore♥

Shemini: I have fallen in love at first
sight with Lady Claudia!!

Shemini: Please, become my partner
without fail♥

Claudia: Um, wait... I can't keep up
with the understanding...

Shemini: Sleepy eyes... a dignified
face... sweet sighs escaping from soft
lips...

Shemini: To everything about Lady
Claudia!
Shemini: You are filled with charm!!

Shemini: I will make you experience
ecstasy!!

Shemini: By all means!! I would like to
date you with marriage as a premise!!

Zerachiel: The reason why this forest
was sealed...
Claudia: ...So this is what it meant.

Shemini: Ahh♥ Your attitude of ignoring
me is also lovely♥

Shemini: Now, please let me impregnate
you with my spores, my dear companion♥
